ACOEngine - Class in TSP.ApproximationAlgorithms.ACO
This class is used to represent the ACS algorithm presented in the Dorigo paper.
ACOEngine() - Constructor for class TSP.ApproximationAlgorithms.ACO.ACOEngine
This is the default constructor and is used to created an instance of the algorithm based on values specified in the Dorigo book.
ACOEngine(Graph) - Constructor for class TSP.ApproximationAlgorithms.ACO.ACOEngine
This constructor is used to create an instance of the algorithm based on default values as the previous constructor , however using the specified graph as parameter
ACOEngine(int, double, double, double, String, int) - Constructor for class TSP.ApproximationAlgorithms.ACO.ACOEngine
This constructor is used to create a new aco algorithm instance based on parameter values as required by the user
AlgorithmLauncher - Class in <Unnamed>
This class contains the main method which is used to start all the algorithms that were developed, to approximate the TSP instances found in the folder MathematicsThesis/src/TSP/GraphInstances.
AlgorithmLauncher() - Constructor for class AlgorithmLauncher
 
Ant - Class in TSP.ApproximationAlgorithms.ACO
This class encodes the artificial ant described in the Dorigo ant system paper, which is used to traverse the graph created using graph instances found in the folder src/TSP/GraphInstances.
Ant() - Constructor for class TSP.ApproximationAlgorithms.ACO.Ant
This default constructor is used to give default values to the newly created ant whenever no parameters are given
Ant(int) - Constructor for class TSP.ApproximationAlgorithms.ACO.Ant
This constructor is used to create a new ant on a particular city specifying the city id as parameter
antCompletedTour(int) - Method in class TSP.ApproximationAlgorithms.ACO.Ant
This method is used in the ACOEngine class to check if the ant has completed the tour
approximateTsp() - Method in class TSP.ApproximationAlgorithms.ACO.ACOEngine
This method is used to start the algorithm
approximateTsp() - Method in class TSP.ApproximationAlgorithms.NearestNeighbourApproximation.NearestNeighbourHeuristicEngine
This method is used to start the algorithm and perform an approximation for the TSP
approximateTSP() - Method in class TSP.ApproximationAlgorithms.TwiceAroundMST.TwiceAroundMSTHeuristic
This method is used to give an approximation of the TSP based on the 2*MST heuristic.
